paragraphs.text:
%redshift

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users
(
  id bigint NOT NULL IDENTITY(1001,1),
  id_str VARCHAR UNIQUE,
  friends_count bigint,
  favourites_count bigint,
  description VARCHAR(max),
  created_at VARCHAR,
  name VARCHAR,
  screen_name VARCHAR(max) ,
  statuses_count bigint,
  location VARCHAR DISTKEY,
  primary key(id)  
)
interleaved sortkey(location,friends_count)

%redshift


CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS tweets 
(
  language VARCHAR NOT NULL,
  retweet_count bigint,
  text VARCHAR(max) NOT NULL,
  quote_count bigint,
  timestamp_ms timestamp NOT NULL,
  created_at VARCHAR NOT NULL,
  source VARCHAR NOT NULL,
  user_id bigint NOT NULL DISTKEY,
  id bigint NOT NULL IDENTITY(2001,1),
  primary key(id),
  foreign key(user_id) references users(id_str)
  )
  interleaved sortkey(language,user_id,source)
